>> HAND CLOW: The Age of what?

00:15:05.710 --> 00:15:06.810 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Was it the Mandaeans?

00:15:06.810 --> 00:15:07.810 align:middle line:90%
>> HAND CLOW: Mandaeans.

00:15:07.810 --> 00:15:11.170 align:middle line:84%
