remnants of the Babylonians.

00:15:11.170 --> 00:15:14.200 align:middle line:84%
And now you're putting in
here, at the opening chapters,

00:15:14.200 --> 00:15:17.240 align:middle line:84%
timelines of what's happening
militarily around the world,

00:15:17.240 --> 00:15:19.282 align:middle line:84%
especially at the hands
of the American military.

00:15:19.282 --> 00:15:20.406 align:middle line:90%
>> HAND CLOW: That's right.

00:15:20.406 --> 00:15:21.970 align:middle line:84%
And also, Regina,
I'd like to say

00:15:21.970 --> 00:15:23.980 align:middle line:84%
that all of the
background information,

00:15:23.980 --> 00:15:27.760 align:middle line:84%
the historical timelines,
the history of religion,

00:15:27.760 --> 00:15:30.060 align:middle line:84%
all of that stuff is totally
factual and totally--

00:15:30.060 --> 00:15:30.930 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Oh, yeah.

00:15:30.930 --> 00:15:34.000 align:middle line:84%
>> HAND CLOW: And then the
characters and the storyline is

00:15:34.000 --> 00:15:35.200 align:middle line:90%
completely fictional.

00:15:35.200 --> 00:15:36.860 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes.

00:15:36.860 --> 00:15:38.670 align:middle line:84%
But the historical
data is accurate.

00:15:38.670 --> 00:15:39.470 align:middle line:90%
Yes.

00:15:39.470 --> 00:15:43.210 align:middle line:84%
And so now, why did--
the Simon character--

00:15:43.210 --> 00:15:46.000 align:middle line:84%
why did you begin
weaving in these stories

00:15:46.000 --> 00:15:51.010 align:middle line:84%
of these various sects,
such as the Mandaeans?

00:15:51.010 --> 00:15:53.170 align:middle line:84%
And talk about them
for a moment and why

00:15:53.170 --> 00:15:56.470 align:middle line:84%
this matters at this point
in time in our history.

00:15:56.470 --> 00:15:58.900 align:middle line:84%
>> HAND CLOW: Well, when the
time timeline on the second

00:15:58.900 --> 00:16:03.130 align:middle line:84%
