00:16:17.700 --> 00:16:20.650 align:middle line:84%
And so one of the
purposes of this trilogy

00:16:20.650 --> 00:16:23.710 align:middle line:84%
is to track the timeline
historically from 2011

00:16:23.710 --> 00:16:28.150 align:middle line:84%
through 2020, because I believe
that this is the vortex turning

00:16:28.150 --> 00:16:31.900 align:middle line:84%
point into the Age of Aquarius
and out of the Age of Pisces.

00:16:31.900 --> 00:16:34.240 align:middle line:84%
So that type of
material is in the book

00:16:34.240 --> 00:16:36.880 align:middle line:84%
so that we could see
what's going away.

00:16:36.880 --> 00:16:39.250 align:middle line:84%
Because for example,
specifically, there

00:16:39.250 --> 00:16:41.440 align:middle line:90%
