00:16:41.440 --> 00:16:44.590 align:middle line:84%
and some people are familiar
with the Copts in Egypt.

00:16:44.590 --> 00:16:47.140 align:middle line:84%
And they also were a Christian
sect-- or the Mandaeans

00:16:47.140 --> 00:16:49.120 align:middle line:90%
and the Druze Christians.

00:16:49.120 --> 00:16:54.030 align:middle line:84%
And in the Middle East, there
are a group of Christian sects.

00:16:54.030 --> 00:16:56.152 align:middle line:84%
And basically,
unknown to Americans--

00:16:56.152 --> 00:16:57.610 align:middle line:84%
what these people
have been doing--

00:16:57.610 --> 00:17:00.151 align:middle line:84%
because they're Christians, and
they're people of the heart--

00:17:00.151 --> 00:17:03.220 align:middle line:84%
