00:17:32.340 --> 00:17:34.090 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: And how did
these other factions

00:17:34.090 --> 00:17:35.090 align:middle line:90%
get caught in the crossfire?

00:17:35.090 --> 00:17:36.881 align:middle line:84%
>> HAND CLOW: Well,
the Christian sects are

