Because as you know, with the
collapse of the automobile

00:18:07.430 --> 00:18:10.550 align:middle line:84%
industry, Detroit, and Flint,
and Saginaw just basically

00:18:10.550 --> 00:18:11.590 align:middle line:90%
were vacant.

00:18:11.590 --> 00:18:14.420 align:middle line:84%
And it's all filled up with
Middle Eastern Christians.

00:18:14.420 --> 00:18:16.734 align:middle line:84%
And they have a really
vibrant culture there.

00:18:16.734 --> 00:18:18.650 align:middle line:84%
And these people are
going all over the world.

00:18:18.650 --> 00:18:21.050 align:middle line:84%
And they're really
wonderful people.

00:18:21.050 --> 00:18:23.270 align:middle line:90%
But I wanted to document that.

00:18:23.270 --> 00:18:24.980 align:middle line:84%
Because I think it's
such a-- speaking

00:18:24.980 --> 00:18:27.860 align:middle line:84%
of the change of the ages and
going out of the Age of Pisces.

00:18:27.860 --> 00:18:31.520 align:middle line:84%
The Age of Pisces was the
age of organized religion.

00:18:31.520 --> 00:18:34.480 align:middle line:84%
And so I wanted to give
information on this

00:18:34.480 --> 00:18:37.220 align:middle line:84%
this transformation
of the organized

00:18:37.220 --> 00:18:38.690 align:middle line:90%
religions of the Age of Pisces.

00:18:38.690 --> 00:18:40.270 align:middle line:84%
So that's why
that's in the book.

00:18:40.270 --> 00:18:43.100 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: And the Marcionites,
as well, another faction.

00:18:43.100 --> 00:18:45.230 align:middle line:84%
And also, you
mentioned the Yazidis,

00:18:45.230 --> 00:18:48.800 align:middle line:84%
But most people aren't clear
exactly who they are, except

00:18:48.800 --> 00:18:51.470 align:middle line:84%
for the role you just said as
providing this kind of grace,

00:18:51.470 --> 00:18:53.900 align:middle line:84%
or this kind of charity,
or something in the region

00:18:53.900 --> 00:18:56.870 align:middle line:84%
to keep the factions off
each other's backs a bit.

00:18:56.870 --> 00:18:59.900 align:middle line:84%
And is that true of all
of the different factions

00:18:59.900 --> 00:19:01.820 align:middle line:84%
of these various
Christian Arabic groups,

00:19:01.820 --> 00:19:02.550 align:middle line:90%
like Marsh Arabs, as you say?

00:19:02.550 --> 00:19:03.675 align:middle line:90%
>> HAND CLOW: No, some are.

00:19:03.675 --> 00:19:08.810 align:middle line:84%
Like, for instance, the Yazidis
are a 10,000-year-old early

00:19:08.810 --> 00:19:09.770 align:middle line:90%
religious sect.

00:19:09.770 --> 00:19:11.580 align:middle line:10%
They aren't really Christian.

00:19:11.580 --> 00:19:13.189 align:middle line:10%
And so what you
heard on the media

00:19:13.189 --> 00:19:14.480 align:middle line:10%
is they were devil worshippers.

00:19:14.480 --> 00:19:16.070 align:middle line:10%
Well, they're not
devil worshippers.

00:19:16.070 --> 00:19:21.080 align:middle line:10%
They're just simply early
really Pagan spiritual people.

00:19:21.080 --> 00:19:25.010 align:middle line:84%
And what most people
know about the Yazidis is

00:19:25.010 --> 00:19:28.200 align:middle line:84%
