00:19:28.200 --> 00:19:31.790 align:middle line:84%
which was actually a genocide
of the Yazidi people.

00:19:31.790 --> 00:19:34.450 align:middle line:84%
So I'm covering these
issues, because--

00:19:34.450 --> 00:19:37.610 align:middle line:84%
OK, here I am writing a
book that's documenting 2011

00:19:37.610 --> 00:19:40.700 align:middle line:84%
through 2020, which, as
you know at this point,

00:19:40.700 --> 00:19:44.180 align:middle line:84%
is one of the most complex
periods in human history.

00:19:44.180 --> 00:19:48.120 align:middle line:84%
And so my issue, as a novelist,
was selection of detail.

00:19:48.120 --> 00:19:51.110 align:middle line:84%
And so these issues
are in there to create

00:19:51.110 --> 00:19:54.020 align:middle line:84%
an understanding of some of the
things that are passing away.

00:19:54.020 --> 00:19:56.840 align:middle line:84%
Because these elements of
Christianity are passing away.

00:19:56.840 --> 00:20:01.250 align:middle line:84%
You can't go in and bomb
countries to flush everybody

00:20:01.250 --> 00:20:02.960 align:middle line:84%
out and make everybody
get on the road

00:20:02.960 --> 00:20:05.030 align:middle line:84%
without creating a
decimation of culture.

00:20:05.030 --> 00:20:06.680 align:middle line:84%
So that's what
we're experiencing.

00:20:06.680 --> 00:20:08.750 align:middle line:84%
And I'm mainly there
to document it.

00:20:08.750 --> 00:20:09.742 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: OK.

00:20:09.742 --> 00:20:11.450 align:middle line:90%
And in amongst this--

00:20:11.450 --> 00:20:13.630 align:middle line:84%
relatively modern
history, anyway--

00:20:13.630 --> 00:20:16.085 align:middle line:84%
you bring in the
Fatima prophecies.

00:20:16.085 --> 00:20:17.210 align:middle line:90%
>> HAND CLOW: That's right.

00:20:17.210 --> 00:20:18.060 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Why?

00:20:18.060 --> 00:20:19.010 align:middle line:90%
>> HAND CLOW: OK.

00:20:19.010 --> 00:20:21.860 align:middle line:84%
Because the Fatima
prophecies are the prophecies

00:20:21.860 --> 00:20:24.500 align:middle line:84%
for the 20th through
21st century.

00:20:24.500 --> 00:20:28.670 align:middle line:84%
And the first two prophecies
of Fatima have been fulfilled.

00:20:28.670 --> 00:20:31.300 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: And please, tell
people what happened then

00:20:31.300 --> 00:20:32.845 align:middle line:90%
and what the prophecies are.

00:20:32.845 --> 00:20:34.970 align:middle line:84%
>> HAND CLOW: Most people
actually know about this.

00:20:34.970 --> 00:20:40.130 align:middle line:84%
This was three Portuguese
girls, two of them quite young.

00:20:40.130 --> 00:20:43.020 align:middle line:84%
And then one of them was seven,
or eight, or nine years old.

00:20:43.020 --> 00:20:45.950 align:middle line:84%
And they saw a bunch
of visions on the edge

00:20:45.950 --> 00:20:48.800 align:middle line:90%
of a hill in Portugal.

00:20:48.800 --> 00:20:51.920 align:middle line:84%
So the oldest one
wrote down the visions.

00:20:51.920 --> 00:20:53.960 align:middle line:84%
And then, as they
started to come true,

00:20:53.960 --> 00:20:56.802 align:middle line:84%
this information was
given to the popes.

00:20:56.802 --> 00:20:58.760 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: What was the
information coming true?

00:20:58.760 --> 00:21:01.230 align:middle line:84%
>> HAND CLOW: Well, this one
girl Portuguese girl wrote it

00:21:01.230 --> 00:21:02.030 align:middle line:90%
down.

00:21:02.030 --> 00:21:05.030 align:middle line:84%
The girls were put in
a nunnery after this.

00:21:05.030 --> 00:21:08.330 align:middle line:84%
