these little girls couldn't

00:21:15.230 --> 00:21:16.730 align:middle line:90%
possibly have known about.

00:21:16.730 --> 00:21:18.770 align:middle line:84%
And then the third
one is hidden.

00:21:18.770 --> 00:21:20.690 align:middle line:84%
And so, of course, I'm
using it in the novel.

00:21:20.690 --> 00:21:22.910 align:middle line:84%
Because the third one
has to do with the end

00:21:22.910 --> 00:21:26.190 align:middle line:84%
of the Age of Pisces
and going into Aquarius.

00:21:26.190 --> 00:21:32.750 align:middle line:84%
And the best speculations that
I've been able to find so far

00:21:32.750 --> 00:21:34.910 align:middle line:84%
are that the third
Fatima prophecy

00:21:34.910 --> 00:21:40.310 align:middle line:84%
is prophesying a apostasy,
which means the emptying

00:21:40.310 --> 00:21:42.940 align:middle line:84%
out of the faithful
out of the church.

00:21:42.940 --> 00:21:46.610 align:middle line:84%
And so the Catholic church
is tremendously diminished

00:21:46.610 --> 00:21:47.600 align:middle line:90%
at this point.

00:21:47.600 --> 00:21:49.610 align:middle line:90%
But I was a Catholic.

00:21:49.610 --> 00:21:52.850 align:middle line:84%
Once you're Catholic,
you're on the roles forever.

00:21:52.850 --> 00:21:55.380 align:middle line:84%
Once you're Catholic,
you're a Catholic forever.

00:21:55.380 --> 00:21:57.110 align:middle line:84%
So the actual
number of Catholics

00:21:57.110 --> 00:21:59.810 align:middle line:84%
who are actually practicing
and actually giving money

00:21:59.810 --> 00:22:01.650 align:middle line:90%
to the church is plummeting.

00:22:01.650 --> 00:22:03.460 align:middle line:84%
And Francis fears
this very much.

00:22:03.460 --> 00:22:05.200 align:middle line:90%
He's said so.

00:22:05.200 --> 00:22:08.050 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yeah.

00:22:08.050 --> 00:22:11.380 align:middle line:84%
