00:23:35.340 --> 00:23:39.220 align:middle line:10%
I actually put that more into
the context of the Age of Aries

00:23:39.220 --> 00:23:40.330 align:middle line:10%
and the Age of Pisces.

00:23:40.330 --> 00:23:41.510 align:middle line:10%
Now what am I talking about?

00:23:41.510 --> 00:23:46.085 align:middle line:10%
Well, the Age of Pisces
is like 160 BC to now.

00:23:46.085 --> 00:23:48.580 align:middle line:84%
Because now we're
going into Aquarius.

00:23:48.580 --> 00:23:52.960 align:middle line:84%
The Age of Aries before the
Age of Pisces is like 2400 BC

00:23:52.960 --> 00:23:56.170 align:middle line:90%
to 200 BC.

00:23:56.170 --> 00:23:58.900 align:middle line:84%
And the Age of Aries
is the age of war.

00:23:58.900 --> 00:24:02.810 align:middle line:84%
And then the Age of Pisces
is the age of wars for God.

00:24:02.810 --> 00:24:06.550 align:middle line:84%
And so at this point, these
are the central issues

00:24:06.550 --> 00:24:08.530 align:middle line:84%
that we have to
have to transform

00:24:08.530 --> 00:24:10.940 align:middle line:90%
and transcend on this planet.

00:24:10.940 --> 00:24:13.120 align:middle line:84%
And so I don't so much
go after the patriarchy.

00:24:13.120 --> 00:24:14.940 align:middle line:84%
Because the
patriarchy is simply--

00:24:14.940 --> 00:24:16.925 align:middle line:84%
we actually find that
we all know it, right?

00:24:16.925 --> 00:24:19.090 align:middle line:84%
We've had 5,000
years patriarchy.

00:24:19.090 --> 00:24:22.810 align:middle line:84%
But now, by fine tuning it
into the changes of the ages,

00:24:22.810 --> 00:24:25.630 align:middle line:84%
you get more of a sense of the
things that need to transform.

00:24:25.630 --> 00:24:28.210 align:middle line:84%
Because the change of the
ages from one to the next--

00:24:28.210 --> 00:24:31.570 align:middle line:84%
we're all really lucky
to be here right now

00:24:31.570 --> 00:24:33.370 align:middle line:84%
to be living at
the end of Pisces

00:24:33.370 --> 00:24:36.850 align:middle line:84%
and moving into Aquarius, even
though the chaos and confusion

00:24:36.850 --> 00:24:38.980 align:middle line:84%
is very, very hard on
all of us, because we're

00:24:38.980 --> 00:24:40.990 align:middle line:84%
going through this
incredible change

00:24:40.990 --> 00:24:43.320 align:middle line:84%
where everything in
culture, everything

00:24:43.320 --> 00:24:44.860 align:middle line:90%
is changing right now.

00:24:44.860 --> 00:24:46.690 align:middle line:84%
And as we're doing
this interview,

00:24:46.690 --> 00:24:49.780 align:middle line:84%
there's huge changes in
NATO, huge changes in lots

00:24:49.780 --> 00:24:51.280 align:middle line:90%
of global organizations.

00:24:51.280 --> 00:24:53.850 align:middle line:84%
Because that's what happens
at the end of an age.

00:24:53.850 --> 00:24:55.480 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: And one of
the things you say

00:24:55.480 --> 00:24:58.330 align:middle line:84%
