of the masculine and feminine

00:25:11.300 --> 00:25:12.100 align:middle line:90%
again.

00:25:12.100 --> 00:25:13.225 align:middle line:90%
>> HAND CLOW: That's right.

00:25:13.225 --> 00:25:16.300 align:middle line:84%
And then I think a
deeper and more important

00:25:16.300 --> 00:25:18.930 align:middle line:90%
contribution from me--

00:25:18.930 --> 00:25:21.670 align:middle line:90%
it's in "Aquarian Age."

00:25:21.670 --> 00:25:24.940 align:middle line:84%
And then I'm working on it even
more so in the current book--

00:25:24.940 --> 00:25:28.610 align:middle line:84%
