00:25:34.150 --> 00:25:36.370 align:middle line:84%
And what has happened
is the religions--

00:25:36.370 --> 00:25:38.410 align:middle line:84%
basically Islam
and Christianity,

00:25:38.410 --> 00:25:41.050 align:middle line:84%
in particular-- have been
at each other's throats.

00:25:41.050 --> 00:25:43.480 align:middle line:84%
And yet, in the novel,
we're going back

00:25:43.480 --> 00:25:47.200 align:middle line:84%
2,000 years ago to what
happened when Jesus

00:25:47.200 --> 00:25:49.820 align:middle line:84%
or when Christ was
on this planet.

00:25:49.820 --> 00:25:52.390 align:middle line:84%
And I'm getting a hold
of the things that

00:25:52.390 --> 00:25:54.010 align:middle line:90%
created the division.

00:25:54.010 --> 00:25:58.600 align:middle line:84%
Because I actually believe that,
if people can see the divisions

00:25:58.600 --> 00:26:01.279 align:middle line:84%
