stop fighting with each other.

00:26:01.279 --> 00:26:03.070 align:middle line:84%
And I think this is
what it's going to take

00:26:03.070 --> 00:26:05.790 align:middle line:90%
to end the wars for God.

00:26:05.790 --> 00:26:06.590 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes.

