>> HAND CLOW: It has
a number of stages.

00:44:12.100 --> 00:44:13.605 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: It had a number of
stages of its destruction.

00:44:13.605 --> 00:44:14.730 align:middle line:90%
>> HAND CLOW: That's right.

00:44:14.730 --> 00:44:17.330 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: And I wasn't really
clear on that part of it,

00:44:17.330 --> 00:44:19.790 align:middle line:84%
except for what happened
in this event, which

00:44:19.790 --> 00:44:23.090 align:middle line:84%
was extremely visceral, more
visceral than being here.

00:44:23.090 --> 00:44:26.210 align:middle line:84%
And in it, what
I was doing was--

00:44:26.210 --> 00:44:28.250 align:middle line:84%
there was a certain
amount of blame going on.

00:44:28.250 --> 00:44:29.780 align:middle line:84%
Because I understood
that there were

00:44:29.780 --> 00:44:33.290 align:middle line:84%
people working with
technology to do something.

00:44:33.290 --> 00:44:35.930 align:middle line:84%
And this was becoming
extraordinarily destabilized.

00:44:35.930 --> 00:44:39.530 align:middle line:84%
I was working with natural
energies along with other women

00:44:39.530 --> 00:44:42.120 align:middle line:84%
to help stabilize what
was going on at the time.

00:44:42.120 --> 00:44:46.720 align:middle line:84%
Now when the event happened--
this was the final day before

00:44:46.720 --> 00:44:47.800 align:middle line:90%
the event--

00:44:47.800 --> 00:44:49.360 align:middle line:90%
I started noticing something.

00:44:49.360 --> 00:44:52.370 align:middle line:90%
And I said, this is interesting.

00:44:52.370 --> 00:44:56.690 align:middle line:84%
There are spacecraft hovering in
the near atmosphere over here.

00:44:56.690 --> 00:44:58.890 align:middle line:90%
They seem to be doing something.

00:44:58.890 --> 00:45:02.260 align:middle line:84%
And maybe they're taking certain
people out of here or whatnot.

00:45:02.260 --> 00:45:04.420 align:middle line:84%
Well, this same
story was invalidated

00:45:04.420 --> 00:45:06.637 align:middle line:84%
by two other people who had
had the same experience.

00:45:06.637 --> 00:45:08.470 align:middle line:84%
So I thought, OK, I
wasn't making things up.

00:45:08.470 --> 00:45:11.900 align:middle line:84%
And it's into Delores' book,
"Convoluted Universe Two."

00:45:11.900 --> 00:45:14.320 align:middle line:10%
But what happened was
this awful feeling

00:45:14.320 --> 00:45:16.150 align:middle line:10%
of having lost so
much that we would

00:45:16.150 --> 00:45:17.830 align:middle line:10%
be completely traumatized.

00:45:17.830 --> 00:45:19.510 align:middle line:84%
And I kept saying
to her, we're going

00:45:19.510 --> 00:45:21.669 align:middle line:84%
to sleep for a
very long time now.

00:45:21.669 --> 00:45:22.710 align:middle line:90%
And we're going to sleep.

00:45:22.710 --> 00:45:24.860 align:middle line:90%
And I was crying at this point.

00:45:24.860 --> 00:45:27.340 align:middle line:84%
Later on, I talked
with some other people

00:45:27.340 --> 00:45:28.820 align:middle line:90%
who experienced this.

00:45:28.820 --> 00:45:30.280 align:middle line:90%
And this is what came up.

00:45:30.280 --> 00:45:32.810 align:middle line:84%
And this is why I
resonate so strongly.

00:45:32.810 --> 00:45:33.961 align:middle line:90%
I was cloistered.

00:45:33.961 --> 00:45:35.710 align:middle line:84%
So I wasn't really
clear what these people

00:45:35.710 --> 00:45:36.920 align:middle line:90%
were doing technologically.

00:45:36.920 --> 00:45:39.070 align:middle line:84%
I just knew that things
were becoming more and more

00:45:39.070 --> 00:45:40.960 align:middle line:90%
destabilized, so to speak.

00:45:40.960 --> 00:45:42.130 align:middle line:90%
And I had kind of a--

00:45:42.130 --> 00:45:44.500 align:middle line:90%
in this time, a blaming of that.

00:45:44.500 --> 00:45:46.000 align:middle line:84%
I don't know if I
did at that time--

00:45:46.000 --> 00:45:47.290 align:middle line:90%
and in this time, a blaming.

00:45:47.290 --> 00:45:51.130 align:middle line:84%
And it was said, no, these
were natural forces that

00:45:51.130 --> 00:45:53.740 align:middle line:84%
were building up over a
very long period of time.

00:45:53.740 --> 00:45:55.330 align:middle line:84%
And I could see,
we had been trying

00:45:55.330 --> 00:45:57.860 align:middle line:84%
to work with that
energy for generations.

00:45:57.860 --> 00:46:00.380 align:middle line:84%
It was building up over a
very long period of time.

00:46:00.380 --> 00:46:03.314 align:middle line:84%
And they were trying to use
technology to subdue it.

00:46:03.314 --> 00:46:05.980 align:middle line:84%
>> HAND CLOW: And this is what's
going on now, isn't it, Regina?

00:46:05.980 --> 00:46:06.720 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Isn't it?

00:46:06.720 --> 00:46:07.520 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHING]

00:46:07.520 --> 00:46:10.250 align:middle line:84%
And I bring it up, because I
thought we were to blame, too.

00:46:10.250 --> 00:46:11.250 align:middle line:90%
And we were not.

00:46:11.250 --> 00:46:11.660 align:middle line:90%
>> HAND CLOW: Yeah.

00:46:11.660 --> 00:46:13.190 align:middle line:84%
And so, right now
on this planet,

00:46:13.190 --> 00:46:15.730 align:middle line:84%
is another reason I
think understanding

00:46:15.730 --> 00:46:17.260 align:middle line:90%
this transition is so important.

00:46:17.260 --> 00:46:19.330 align:middle line:84%
Because I think the
transition to Aquarius

00:46:19.330 --> 00:46:20.590 align:middle line:90%
is going to be different.

00:46:20.590 --> 00:46:24.010 align:middle line:84%
I do not see major
cataclysmic destruction

00:46:24.010 --> 00:46:25.450 align:middle line:90%
as you go into Aquarius.

00:46:25.450 --> 00:46:27.250 align:middle line:84%
But we're certainly
going to be dealing

00:46:27.250 --> 00:46:30.550 align:middle line:84%
with a lot of climate change
and a lot of cyclical change.

00:46:30.550 --> 00:46:33.440 align:middle line:84%
And there are going to be
cataclysmic things that

00:46:33.440 --> 00:46:34.240 align:middle line:90%
happen--

00:46:34.240 --> 00:46:35.830 align:middle line:84%
nothing like what
happened before.

00:46:35.830 --> 00:46:36.430 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Nothing
like that, yeah.

00:46:36.430 --> 00:46:38.310 align:middle line:84%
>> HAND CLOW: So I'm
covering it in the book.

00:46:38.310 --> 00:46:40.150 align:middle line:84%
In the third book,
I'm going more deeply

00:46:40.150 --> 00:46:42.542 align:middle line:84%
into what's going
on now in terms

00:46:42.542 --> 00:46:44.500 align:middle line:84%
of how to handle what's
actually happening now.

00:46:44.500 --> 00:46:46.780 align:middle line:84%
Because it's really starting
to roll at this point.

00:46:46.780 --> 00:46:48.430 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: And we only have
a couple minutes left.

00:46:48.430 --> 00:46:50.350 align:middle line:84%
But a lot of this takes
place in the backdrop

00:46:50.350 --> 00:46:54.070 align:middle line:84%
of the city of Siena, which
is an interesting city.

00:46:54.070 --> 00:46:57.660 align:middle line:90%
I felt, when I was in Siena--

00:46:57.660 --> 00:46:58.510 align:middle line:90%
I love the Duomo.

00:46:58.510 --> 00:46:59.680 align:middle line:90%
It's so beautiful.

00:46:59.680 --> 00:47:01.860 align:middle line:84%
But I just felt a heaviness
and darkness there.

00:47:01.860 --> 00:47:02.710 align:middle line:84%
>> HAND CLOW: This
is a heaviness there.

00:47:02.710 --> 00:47:04.520 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: -- that I
didn't want to stay in.

00:47:04.520 --> 00:47:07.920 align:middle line:84%
And so my son and I beat it out
of town after a couple of days.

00:47:07.920 --> 00:47:10.310 align:middle line:84%
And I was so surprised
to see, in the book,

00:47:10.310 --> 00:47:12.394 align:middle line:84%
you write about the energies
of the city of Siena.

00:47:12.394 --> 00:47:13.768 align:middle line:84%
>> HAND CLOW:
Yeah, that's right.

00:47:13.768 --> 00:47:16.290 align:middle line:84%
Because the energies of
Siena are very, very major

00:47:16.290 --> 00:47:17.680 align:middle line:90%
and also Orvieto--

00:47:17.680 --> 00:47:19.240 align:middle line:90%
more so in the third book.

00:47:19.240 --> 00:47:22.610 align:middle line:84%
Because there's this issue
of Calleman's midline

00:47:22.610 --> 00:47:24.872 align:middle line:84%
and being a major
geological change--

00:47:24.872 --> 00:47:26.080 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Carl Calleman, yes.

00:47:26.080 --> 00:47:26.380 align:middle line:90%
>> HAND CLOW: --on the planet.

00:47:26.380 --> 00:47:27.700 align:middle line:90%
Carl Calleman, right.

00:47:27.700 --> 00:47:29.127 align:middle line:90%
And it goes right through Italy.

00:47:29.127 --> 00:47:30.710 align:middle line:84%
And it goes right
through this region.

00:47:30.710 --> 00:47:33.250 align:middle line:84%
It goes through Rome,
Orvieto, and Siena.

00:47:33.250 --> 00:47:36.190 align:middle line:84%
So what you're feeling really
is the energy of the midline.

00:47:36.190 --> 00:47:38.590 align:middle line:84%
But in Siena, there's
also some extra energy,

00:47:38.590 --> 00:47:42.595 align:middle line:84%
which I'm going into
more in the third book.

00:47:42.595 --> 00:47:43.470 align:middle line:90%
You're right, though.

00:47:43.470 --> 00:47:44.303 align:middle line:90%
You picked up on it.

00:47:44.303 --> 00:47:46.930 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Oh, yeah, well,
I'm super energy sensitive.

00:47:46.930 --> 00:47:50.320 align:middle line:84%
And I love the fact
that I could have access

00:47:50.320 --> 00:47:51.994 align:middle line:90%
to so much information.

00:47:51.994 --> 00:47:53.410 align:middle line:84%
Because of what I
do for a living,

00:47:53.410 --> 00:47:55.720 align:middle line:84%
so much of what I've
already been exposed to,

00:47:55.720 --> 00:47:59.140 align:middle line:84%
true-- some new, but all
brought together in one place

00:47:59.140 --> 00:48:02.170 align:middle line:84%
through these intelligent,
savvy characters.

00:48:02.170 --> 00:48:04.140 align:middle line:84%
So you did it in a
very effective way.

00:48:04.140 --> 00:48:07.505 align:middle line:84%
And at the very end of the book,
many revelations have come up.

00:48:07.505 --> 00:48:08.380 align:middle line:90%
They're all together.

00:48:08.380 --> 00:48:10.530 align:middle line:84%
And they say, we
must meet again.

00:48:10.530 --> 00:48:11.330 align:middle line:90%
Boom.

00:48:11.330 --> 00:48:12.746 align:middle line:84%
And I'm thinking,
oh, I can't wait

00:48:12.746 --> 00:48:15.160 align:middle line:84%
to see Barbara and pick her
brain at dinner about what

00:48:15.160 --> 00:48:16.220 align:middle line:90%
the new storyline is all about.

00:48:16.220 --> 00:48:17.110 align:middle line:84%
>> HAND CLOW: I don't
know where it's going.

00:48:17.110 --> 00:48:18.715 align:middle line:90%
I'm just letting it happen.

00:48:18.715 --> 00:48:19.900 align:middle line:90%
And it's happening.

00:48:19.900 --> 00:48:21.400 align:middle line:84%
I don't even know
what the title is.

00:48:21.400 --> 00:48:23.200 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Well, I'm really
glad you took up fiction.

00:48:23.200 --> 00:48:24.081 align:middle line:90%
That's all I can say.

00:48:24.081 --> 00:48:25.330 align:middle line:90%
>> HAND CLOW: Well, thank you.

00:48:25.330 --> 00:48:27.130 align:middle line:84%
A lot of people have
rebelled against this.

00:48:27.130 --> 00:48:30.310 align:middle line:84%
But gradually, piece by piece,
they're starting to realize--

00:48:30.310 --> 00:48:32.290 align:middle line:84%
like, I'm not only
doing the same thing,

00:48:32.290 --> 00:48:34.690 align:middle line:84%
but I'm now doing it in
a multi-dimensional way.

00:48:34.690 --> 00:48:38.680 align:middle line:84%
Because the ultimate effect
of taking this information in

00:48:38.680 --> 00:48:41.980 align:middle line:84%
is you're starting to
activate different dimensions

00:48:41.980 --> 00:48:43.210 align:middle line:90%
in your consciousness.

00:48:43.210 --> 00:48:45.580 align:middle line:84%
And I firmly believe, as
a teacher and a healer,

00:48:45.580 --> 00:48:47.215 align:middle line:90%
that we must do this now.

00:48:47.215 --> 00:48:48.440 align:middle line:90%
This is the most important.

00:48:48.440 --> 00:48:48.670 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: We must.

00:48:48.670 --> 00:48:50.980 align:middle line:84%
>> HAND CLOW: We talked about
that in the interview yesterday

00:48:50.980 --> 00:48:52.150 align:middle line:90%
about why that's so important.

00:48:52.150 --> 00:48:52.950 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: We did.

00:48:52.950 --> 00:48:55.150 align:middle line:84%
And we have to live this
reality through our bodies.

00:48:55.150 --> 00:48:57.790 align:middle line:84%
>> HAND CLOW: People want Gerry
and I to show up and just teach

00:48:57.790 --> 00:48:59.040 align:middle line:90%
workshops for everybody.

00:48:59.040 --> 00:49:01.146 align:middle line:84%
But we can't teach
workshops for everybody,

00:49:01.146 --> 00:49:02.770 align:middle line:84%
although we're going
to do what we can.

00:49:02.770 --> 00:49:05.080 align:middle line:10%
So that's why I wrote a
fictional trilogy in order

00:49:05.080 --> 00:49:08.560 align:middle line:10%
to help people experience
multi-dimensionality

00:49:08.560 --> 00:49:09.890 align:middle line:10%
through these characters.

00:49:09.890 --> 00:49:10.690 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Indeed.

00:49:10.690 --> 00:49:12.040 align:middle line:90%
Well, you've done a lovely job.

00:49:12.040 --> 00:49:14.130 align:middle line:84%
And I can't wait
for the third one.

00:49:14.130 --> 00:49:15.130 align:middle line:90%
>> HAND CLOW: Thank you.

00:49:15.130 --> 00:49:18.440 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: What year is the
third one coming out, 2019?

00:49:18.440 --> 00:49:20.924 align:middle line:84%
>> HAND CLOW: No, because the
timeline's 2018 through 2020.

00:49:20.924 --> 00:49:22.840 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: So does it
have to come out in 2020?

00:49:22.840 --> 00:49:24.756 align:middle line:84%
>> HAND CLOW: It has
to come out in 2021.

00:49:24.756 --> 00:49:25.210 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: OK.

00:49:25.210 --> 00:49:27.040 align:middle line:84%
>> HAND CLOW: Because we've
got to finish the timeline.

00:49:27.040 --> 00:49:28.940 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: OK, so we have
a couple of years to wait.

00:49:28.940 --> 00:49:29.740 align:middle line:90%
OK.

00:49:29.740 --> 00:49:30.890 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHING]

00:49:30.890 --> 00:49:32.050 align:middle line:90%
Again, thank you, Barbara.

00:49:32.050 --> 00:49:34.587 align:middle line:84%
As always, it's absolutely
wonderful sitting with you.

00:49:34.587 --> 00:49:35.920 align:middle line:90%
>> HAND CLOW: Thank you, Regina.

00:49:35.920 --> 00:49:37.920 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Again, the name
of Barbara's new novel

00:49:37.920 --> 00:49:39.760 align:middle line:84%
is "Revelations of the
Aquarian Age," which

00:49:39.760 --> 00:49:41.852 align:middle line:84%
introduced a great deal
of little-known esoteric

00:49:41.852 --> 00:49:43.060 align:middle line:90%
knowledge, as you just heard.

00:49:43.060 --> 00:49:46.140 align:middle line:10%
You can find it at major
booksellers, as well as

00:49:46.140 --> 00:49:49.110 align:middle line:10%
the previous book, "Revelations
of the Ruby Crystal."

00:49:49.110 --> 00:49:51.180 align:middle line:10%
Until next time, thank
you for joining us here

00:49:51.180 --> 00:49:53.240 align:middle line:10%
on "Open Minds."

